 package that contains all the binaries, files and dependencies required to run
 a given command on the author's computational environment (packing step). A
 reviewer can then extract the experiment in his environment to reproduce the
 results (unpacking step).
 .
 This package contains the reprounzip program, used to unpack experiments.

